{
  "title": "心意相通",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "樱花",
      "text": "（沉默了很久，然后轻轻点了点头）……嗯。",
      "background": "G0/image-back/bg_library.png",
      "background_prompt": "",
      "voice": "",
      "background_music": "",
      "characters": [
        {
          "image": "G0/image-person/char_sakura_happy.jpg",
          "image_prompt": "",
          "motion": "still"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "character": "旁白",
      "text": "窗外，樱花花瓣随风飘落，阳光将图书馆染成了金色。",
      "background": "G0/image-back/bg_library.png",
      "background_prompt": "",
      "voice": "",
      "background_music": "",
      "characters": [
        {
          "image": "G0/image-person/char_sakura_happy.jpg",
          "image_prompt": "",
          "motion": "still"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "character": "你",
      "text": "那……我也有话想对你说。从昨天开始，我就一直在想你。",
      "background": "G0/image-back/bg_library.png",
      "background_prompt": "",
      "voice": "",
      "background_music": "",
      "characters": [
        {
          "image": "G0/image-person/char_sakura_happy.jpg",
          "image_prompt": "",
          "motion": "still"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "character": "樱花",
      "text": "（眼眶微微泛红，嘴角却忍不住上扬）……真是的，你这个人……",
      "background": "G0/image-back/bg_library.png",
      "background_prompt": "",
      "voice": "",
      "background_music": "",
      "characters": [
        {
          "image": "G0/image-person/char_sakura_happy.jpg",
          "image_prompt": "",
          "motion": "still"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "character": "旁白",
      "text": "那天下午，你们在图书馆里待到了夕阳西下。书架之间，两颗心悄悄靠近，如同春日里盛开的樱花，美丽而短暂，却又令人难以忘怀。",
      "background": "G0/image-back/bg_library.png",
      "background_prompt": "",
      "voice": "",
      "background_music": "",
      "characters": [
        {
          "image": "G0/image-person/char_sakura_happy.jpg",
          "image_prompt": "",
          "motion": "still"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "character": "旁白",
      "text": "这一刻，你知道——这段故事，才刚刚开始。",
      "background": "G0/image-back/bg_library.png",
      "background_prompt": "",
      "voice": "",
      "background_music": "",
      "characters": [
        {
